msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/cdi.adoc:139
msgid "A qualifier type is a Java annotation defined as `@Retention(RUNTIME)` and annotated with the `@javax.inject.Qualifier` meta-annotation:"
